

=Bio=

"Pierre W. Johnson is a researcher and author on fair trade and solidarity economy. He is the founder of Solecopedia.org global shared dictionary of solidarity economy and ecological economics. His books on Fair Trade and alternatives to Biopiracy are opensource, and published by Charles Léopold Mayer Editor. He defends opensource and a transition perspective on the economy, which includes the rehabilitation of the commons and the inclusion of economy in living systems."


